{"tid":1361544,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"「吃喝無罪，玩樂有你」Tg活動谷招會然","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T08:49:03.000Z","uid":94946,"like":4,"dislike":131,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab0121aca1b594292216fc9757fa57d601fa77db","tid":1361544,"uid":94946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:35:22.000Z","msg":"歡迎加入我哋一分子～<br />\n<br />\n本谷會定期舉辦活動，如boardgame聚、飯局、party等，結集不同背景和年齡層嘅朋友，適合想識朋友又怕悶嘅你。<br />\n本谷唔介意同其他谷聯合活動，會然亦可提議或自行舉辦活動。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅你可以填寫下表，admin將會盡快加你入谷。為控制人數，將不定期清潛，盼能迎來活躍的你^^<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1B2RJwoy9Gm3G68pupzNMrYGgulmnjRjE0gOMuhFX2UU/viewform?edit_requested=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1B2RJwoy9Gm3G68pupzNMrYGgulmnjRjE0gOMuhFX2UU%2Fviewform%3Fedit_requested%3Dtrue&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0IE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=9ad536b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1B2RJwoy9Gm3G68pupzNMrYGgulmnjRjE0gOMuhFX2UU/viewform?edit_requested=true</a>"},{"pid":"aa4fd111a6962481e22941560e200aafc5e7d8ba","tid":1361544,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要！唔該幫手推啊！！推得好辛苦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa6ae8c1f6bce6d7e73562a9cb1d5716d06840f8","tid":1361544,"uid":94946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ed2de0381e5fb88f710644b2a3b81642cad7e816","tid":1361544,"uid":286276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8f9